{"tid":1767671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[積極行動POST] 12.8 維園見","createTime":"2019-12-03T13:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T12:55:41.000Z","uid":239351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8213f92dedeaf05c739e1c7505ce0bfcfbbd8778","tid":1767671,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"過去呢幾個月，大家都以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">憤怒</span></span>作為遊行集會嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">動力</span></span>。冇錯，我地五大訴求未得到答應，好多醜陋嘅人權問題未得清算。甚至你有朋友被濫捕，要報到，要去打官司，你身邊嘅手足入醫院。<br />\n<br />\n區選從來都係一個支線任務。打贏一個副本係一件開心事，過份開心對打最終主線大佬並無幫助。呢一點我無意改變。打主線所受嘅傷我地應該銘記於心。<br />\n<br />\n我要提出今個星期<span style=\"color: gold;\">遊行集會</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">區選</span>同有一個共通點：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用人數去表態</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n早兩個星期用人數表咗一次態，今個星期我地再用人數去表態。兩件事本質相近。因為我地已知有好多人同我地同路，我想提出我地可以轉為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以積極面對</span></span>，用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">積極去作為動力</span></span>。我地可以有七成投票率，可唔可以有高嘅集會遊行出席率？<br />\n<br />\n積極<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔係忘記苦楚</span>，而係<span style=\"color: gold;\">對前境抱有希望</span>。我地<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔係為贏咗區選</span>而抱有希望，而係為我地<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有好多人一齊表態</span></span>而抱有希望。<br />\n<br />\n應承我，星期日一齊出嚟。望一望左邊，望一望右邊，佢地都係兩個星期前都一齊同你投票嘅人，或者好希望未來同大家一齊投票嘅人。相信你嘅出席可以安慰同支援到身邊嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HpqBst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HpqBst.jpg&h=797b098a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71201e291e1b9d0177817861745dad9161d75af5","tid":1767671,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"我睇返我寫嘅野，我無意指控大家以往消極。只係見到大家似乎熱情冷卻，想嘗試扭轉一下大家對今次集會遊行睇法。"},{"pid":"32b3e15d6f65d08a7977131ae8b07692708f832d","tid":1767671,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63185d577c93d7a3d15a2e2dd516cef53ebdbfe2","tid":1767671,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"12.8當日試試別說「我要雙普選」，改說「我要三普選」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767675/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767675/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9f6f7b075e8135bc9887bdbcbd4388ec3ff6e823","tid":1767671,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3948fec6ac5cd178cc3dd74244d4f2d49495f736","tid":1767671,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57aac43cb22bb01b9a39f212e837a5a357b0b7ce","tid":1767671,"uid":710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7537adf79a96a785bc1e90f6c37b2f5233934c4","tid":1767671,"uid":178115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}